Timberly said my daughter was borderline everyrhing but only so she could bill my insurance ans have me draf my daughyer there once a week. This woman is nothing but a hustler and a horrible person for taking asvantage of this first time mom who was freaking out. She completely took advantage of me. She owes me $550 and i should report her to my insurance
